title: Ep 58 - The Dark Side of the Force
description: Yeah the Jedis are cool, but do they have it all figured out? Maybe the Sith know how to party, too. In this episode of That's Deep Bro I examine what the dark side of the force is and how it can be used to your benefit. I discuss Deborah Ford's book "Dark Side of the Light Chasers".
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
